OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy with a few spots
OL,6,Fof light rain, but some drier,
OL,7,Fbrighter spells developing for a time.
OL,8,FShowery outbreaks of rain will then
OL,9,Fdevelop through the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA rather cloudy evening with
OL,12,Fa few showery outbreaks of rain
OL,13,Fspreading northeast. The rain will be
OL,14,Fmostly light and patchy, but perhaps
OL,15,Fheavier for a time in the evening.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FA rather cloudy start to
OL,18,Fthe morning with patchy light rain.
OL,19,FTurning brighter through the day with
OL,20,Fsunny spells and scattered showers,
OL,21,Fone or two on the heavier side.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
